I"~<h4 id="situation">Situation</h4>
<ul>
  <li>The client was a $10B oil and gas company, spanning nine product lines and seven regions</li>
  <li>The organization had no centralized commercial organization despite increasing reliance on cross-regional and cross-product line projects</li>
  <li>Lack of consistent processes, policies and organizations</li>
  <li>Existing commercial organizations relied heavily on a select number of ‘heroes’ with a wide range of local organizational maturity</li>
  <li>The organization was losing market share at the same time as continued price deflation for their products and services</li>
</ul>
